。 六辻的文章指出，牛油果引发注目的契机，是 1997 年美国解禁墨西哥产的牛油果。从那年开始，牛油果在美国的市场急速扩张，当时的美国，对于健康、有机产品的追求成为一种社会风潮。在这种背景下，牛油果在美国的市场急速扩张。 详细报道：爱吃牛油果的美国人，正在摧毁自己口中的「环保」？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-d2b5c0f22fb62fc36e71fd10152422b1_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "420 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/466723204"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I0uCoiY34s8svEAMaCDY1OTk1NjA0IKLKyoYGMA44sgFADHIJNDY2NzIzMjA0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1624446357.1086025", "card_id": "Q_319790208", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 48}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "「物理学的大厦已经落成，上面只有两朵乌云」是什么意思？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "19 世纪最后一天，开尔文爵士说「物理学的大厦已经落成，上面只有两朵乌云」。大厦里有什么，两朵乌云是什么？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-59063ab041d55cb0f6f71de216f201dd_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "411 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/319790208"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I0uCoiY34s8svEAMaCDMzMzQwNDcwIOuDwOUFMAg43QdADXIJMzE5NzkwMjA4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1624446357.109068", "card_id": "Q_466591417", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 242}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2021 LPL 夏季赛 RA 2:1 TES，如何评价这场比赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-da4eaca4f966939c83c66585a48aa08c.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "409 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/466591417"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I0uCoiY34s8svEAMaCDY1OTY2NDUzINToxoYGMA04gANADnIJNDY2NTkxNDE3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1624446357.109494", "card_id": "Q_466375037", "feed_specific": 